      "span_id": "p196_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0002",
      "text": " 177",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0003",
      "text": "a) T_server is the value received from the Clock Synchronization Server",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        57.65,
        429.04,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0004",
      "text": "b) T_fabric_delay is the time from when a given value was received from the server until the cor-",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        82.97,
        540.09,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0005",
      "text": "responding value is delivered to the client",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        94.97,
        305.66,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0006",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        118.97,
        114.35,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0007",
      "text": "CS_Accuracy_Mantissa is a value from 000b to 111b'",
      "bbox": [
        122.37,
        118.97,
        359.25,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0008",
      "text": "d) CS_Accuracy_Exponent is a value from 00000b to 11111b'",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        142.96,
        383.68,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0009",
      "text": "Example #1, if CS_Transfer_Accuracy Mantissa and Exponent are set to 001b and 01011b, respec-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        540.11,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0010",
      "text": "tively, the Clock Synchronization value supplied to the clients shall always be within the range of: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        525.95,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0011",
      "text": "(T_server + T_fabric_delay)  ",
      "bbox": [
        120.0,
        202.96,
        248.6,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0012",
      "text": "± ",
      "bbox": [
        248.58,
        201.97,
        256.52,
        214.16
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0013",
      "text": "1,073 ",
      "bbox": [
        256.56,
        202.96,
        284.36,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0014",
      "text": "μ",
      "bbox": [
        284.34,
        201.97,
        290.08,
        214.16
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 4
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0015",
      "text": "sec ",
      "bbox": [
        290.1,
        202.96,
        308.4,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 5
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0016",
      "text": "Example #2, if CS_Transfer_Accuracy Mantissa and Exponent are set to 111b and 11000b, respec-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        540.11,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0017",
      "text": "tively, the Clock Synchronization value supplied to the clients shall always be within the range of: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        525.95,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0018",
      "text": "(T_server + T_fabric_delay)  ",
      "bbox": [
        120.0,
        262.96,
        248.6,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0019",
      "text": "± ",
      "bbox": [
        248.58,
        261.97,
        256.52,
        274.16
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0020",
      "text": "14,65 msec",
      "bbox": [
        256.56,
        262.96,
        308.24,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0021",
      "text": "6.6.9.2.3  Clock Synchronization Implemented MSB",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        337.64,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0022",
      "text": "The Clock Synchronization Implemented MSB field (word 62, bits 13 - 8) is a 6-bit value that repre-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        539.92,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0023",
      "text": "sents the most significant bit position within the 64-bit Clock Count field that contains meaningful in-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        539.99,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0024",
      "text": "formation (e.g., a value of 110111b indicates that the MSB of byte 1 of the Clock Count field is the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        539.98,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0025",
      "text": "highest bit that contains meaningful information).  Word 62, bits 15-14 are reserved and shall be set",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        540.08,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0026",
      "text": "to zero.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        129.29,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0027",
      "text": "This field refers to the capabilities of the Fabric in transferring the clock synchronization value that",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        382.96,
        539.99,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0028",
      "text": "was received from the Clock Synchronization Server (i.e., FFFFF6h) to the clients.  It does not refer",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        540.03,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0029",
      "text": "to the capabilities of the Clock Synchronization Server itself.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        360.9,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0030",
      "text": "6.6.9.2.4  Word 0, Bits 7-0 Clock Synchronization Implemented LSB",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        413.69,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0031",
      "text": "This Clock Synchronization Implemented LSB field (word 62, bits 5 - 0) is a 6-bit value that repre-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        539.96,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0032",
      "text": "sents the least significant bit position within the 64-bit Clock Count field that contains meaningful in-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        540.0,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0033",
      "text": "formation (e.g a value of 001000b indicates that the LSB of byte 6 of the Clock Count field is the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        539.82,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0034",
      "text": "lowest bit that contains meaningful information).  Word 62, bits 7-6 are reserved and shall be set to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        539.86,
        502.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0035",
      "text": "zero.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        118.2,
        514.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0036",
      "text": "This field refers to the capabilities of the Fabric in transferring the clock synchronization value that",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        539.99,
        538.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0037",
      "text": "was received from the Clock Synchronization Server (i.e., FFFFF6h) to the clients.  It does not refer",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        540.03,
        550.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p196_s0038",
      "text": "to the capabilities of the Clock Synchronization Server itself.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        360.9,
        562.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
